                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-11-01T00:15:07.548+09:00">Qín mobilised an army to move in on Zhōu in order to claim the Nine Tripods.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_036-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-10-31T22:19:48.976+09:00">姚宏注：臨，猶伐也。</seg>
